{"tid":1246061,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日就係義士頭七","createTime":"2019-06-20T14:19:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T15:19:30.000Z","uid":63561,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4a2fff31c622b18f8c7d0732056a5b41d94fc52e","tid":1246061,"uid":63561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T14:19:23.000Z","msg":"聽日(6.21)就係反送中義士頭七，傍晚係太古廣場路邊會有路祭緬懷英魂，據<br />\n了解金鐘道大約1930起會有來回封閉措施配合。<br />\n<br />\n今個禮拜發生左好多事，唔同階層嘅香港人為左捍衛自己嘅既有生活方式、價值出左嚟發聲，好多人覺醒左見盡邊個係人邊個係鬼。雖然對於事態嘅發展都啲氣餒、無力感，但希望大家聽日可以出嚟悼念返為我地/我地未來付出左性命嘅義士<br />\n<br />\n大家識做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n和平理性<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好阻人放工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n發夢會有好多人到場悼念義士，迫到出馬路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3a9e84de52098bbe2577136884822177b87e376","tid":1246061,"uid":63561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T15:12:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"640cf57d57689f4335fb5f075e90bd410dc6b661","tid":1246061,"uid":209609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T15:19:30.000Z","msg":"上次讓人放工已經證明咗冇用。今次大家識做啦"}]}